                            <comment id="55236" author="jaylan" created="Mon, 1 Apr 2013 22:14:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Not sure if this &quot;NUMA aware&quot; patch helps Lustre BZ-23047 &quot;zone_reclaim_mode = 1 tanks lustre performance on clients&quot;, so please advise. Appreciated!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;My understanding of the BZ-23047 problem was that zone_reclaim tried to free cache memory aggressively but failed since Lustre held a lock of those clean cache. Without freeing those clean cache, memory allocation may have to grab from nodes of some distance.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
